      "side": 1,
      "message": "maybe also log if final build !\u003d final transmitted build datagram? e.g. if the user executable tries sending some invalid datagrams so the \u0027last thing sent\u0027 !\u003d \u0027last thing seen by runbuild\u0027",
      "range": {
